      • isFinalFragment

        boolean isFinalFragment()
        Check whether the message is a final fragment.
        This is true if the user receives single messages and not a fragments of a message. So if the user is pretty sure that the messages receiving are single messages user does not have to use this method.
        Returns:
        true if the received binary data is a final fragment.
